{"tid":556545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大埔翻巴士】工會批九巴安排文職員工做司機 斥「情況失控」","createTime":"2018-02-10T14:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T14:25:50.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a94c64aba975da473557f1abb4d49a63e102e61c","tid":556545,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:20:32.000Z","msg":"巴士業職工會聯盟晚上近9時發稿對872號九巴翻車意外深表遺憾，並對死傷家屬慰問，但同時表示政府、巴士公司多年來未有正面回應聯盟訴求，表示不滿。<br />\n<br />\n職工聯盟指巴士行業人手緊張、工時長、收入低等問題，事故的司機是一名兼職車長，聯盟促政府加強監管兼職車長的工作安排，又批評九巴最近加強聘請兼職車長、大量安排文職員工駕駛巴士，形容是「情況失控」。反映行業人手不足問題，批評運輸署、運房局「充耳不聞」，致巴士意外一再發生。<br />\n<br />\n工會指，曾就《巴士車長工作指引》促請政府作檢討，但事隔5個月，政府沒有就檢討的時間表仍未交代。工會最後促修改車長工作指引，減工時、加低薪，設立工資指引，吸引新血入行等措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180210/57817851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F57817851&d=unVR8z12bICcBFOPS9zu%2BuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=2f844030\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F57817851&h=397ef761\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180210/57817851</a>"},{"pid":"64e634fc1cb78657680e7bc6c6819e8ef947ca2c","tid":556545,"uid":70575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/222409_7af57f5ce1625a4157d72fa027e7f770.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F222409_7af57f5ce1625a4157d72fa027e7f770.png&h=05f2d42c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}